text: An Incident that no one noticed () is a 1967 Soviet movie directed by Aleksandr Volodin.Детство Мартина Лютера Кинга, кухня КНДР и старинные ситцы. Планы на вечер пятницыПРОИСШЕСТВИЕ, КОТОРОГО НИКТО НЕ ЗАМЕТИЛ It stars Zhanna Prokhorenko, Vera Titova, and Yevgeny Lebedev. == Actors == * Zhanna Prokhorenko as Nastya * Vera Titova as Mother * Yevgeny Lebedev as Yakov Alexeyevich (as Yevgeni Lebedev) * Vitali Solomin as Tolya * Georgiy Shtil as Lyosha * Zinaida Slavina as Katya * Pavel Luspekayev as Teterin == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1967 movies
